{"type":"data","nodes":[{"type":"data","data":[{"debug":1},true],"uses":{}},{"type":"data","data":[{"museum":1,"inscriptions":15},{"slug":2,"type":3,"name":4,"uri":5,"description":6,"location":7},"092","museum","Polimuseo Attilio Zarino","http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/museum/092","A small but relatively rich collection of material from the area around Vittoria. Some are labelled as being from Camarina, some from closer to the museum. There is an inscription, some pottery, some coins and a few other miscellaneous objects. The collection has been declared and gifted to the state, and it is hoped that it will soon be moved to a building designed specifically for it",{"settlement":8,"region":9,"country":10,"address":11,"geo":12},"Vittoria","Ragusa","Italy","piazza Enriquez 15, 97019 - Vittoria (RG)",{"lat":13,"lon":14},36.94792187,14.5410262,[16],{"file":17,"uri":17,"title":18,"status":19,"editionAuthor":21,"type":27,"objectType":31,"material":35,"condition":39,"layoutDesc":41,"handNote":49,"date":61,"places":66,"geo":70,"provenance":8,"provenanceGeo":74,"country":10,"region":77,"settlement":8,"repository":78,"textLang":79,"tmNumber":48,"facsimile":83,"letterHeights":90,"publications":91,"zotero":93,"keywords":95,"html":104,"idnoSort":105,"languageSort":80,"materialSort":36,"originSort":8,"typeSort":28},"ISic003688","Epitaph for Charinos",{"_":20},"edited",{"name":22,"resp":26},{"_":23,"xml:id":24,"ref":25},"Jonathan Prag","JP","http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537","original data collection and editing",{"_":28,"ana":29,"ref":30},"funerary","#function.funerary","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/typeins/lod/92.html",{"_":32,"ana":33,"ref":34},"stele","#object.stele","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/objtyp/lod/250.html",{"_":36,"ana":37,"ref":38},"limestone","#material.stone.limestone","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/material/lod6.html",{"ana":40},"#condition.complete",{"layout":42},{"p":43,"rs":44,"damage":48},"The text occupies five lines, filling the available epigraphic field, with a consistent left margin, except for the centred numeral on line 4.",{"_":45,"ana":46,"ref":47},"chiselled","#execution.chiselled","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/writing/lod/1","",{"lettering":50,"dimensions":51},"Regular letters, neatly cut, with a wide module. Alpha with broken bar and extended right hasta; beta with large round eyes, not quite closed; epsilon of regular quadrate form with equal bars; Kapp with full length arms; Mu with vertical first and last, middle strokes descending no more than halfway; rhomboid omicron; rho with round closed eye and with angular closed eye; lunate but quadrate sigma. Large elegant hedera in final line.",[52,57],{"type":53,"l":54,"from":55,"to":55,"unit":56},"letterHeight","Line 1","line1","mm",{"type":58,"l":59,"from":55,"to":60,"unit":56},"interlinear","Interlineation line 1 to 2","line2",{"_":62,"notBefore":63,"notAfter":64,"evidence":65},"later Roman",301,500,"lettering",[67],{"_":8,"type":68,"ref":69},"modern","http://sws.geonames.org/2522713",[71],[72,73],36.95151,14.52788,[75,76],36.929038,14.531914,"Sicily",{"_":4,"role":3,"ref":5},{"_":80,"mainLang":81,"languages":82},"Ancient Greek","grc",[80],{"n":84,"url":85,"height":86,"width":87,"desc":88,"surfaceType":89},"screen","ISic003688_tiled.tif","3264px","1836px","I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo M. Metcalfe 2015-12-28","front",[],[92],"Lavore, 1983, L’epigrafe di Charinos: lettura e prospettive di studio",[94],"ZKQDM7TJ",[96,97,98,28,32,36,99,100,101,99,102,103,81],"isic003688","epitaph for charinos",{"_":20},"vittoria","italy","sicily","polimuseo attilio zarino","ancient greek","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type